enhanced_by.reason: The processSchemaQueue method must be invoked before getChangedSchemas to ensure that all schema operations are processed and their results are available.
The addSchema method populates the cache with schema operations, which are then filtered and returned by getChangedSchemas.
The getOperations method returns all schema operations, which can be used to construct assertions about the state of the cache before calling getChangedSchemas.
The isPresent method from PendingChanged can be used to assert that the schema operations have been processed and their results are available.
